		<type>ST</type>
		<weight>4</weight>
		<text>Requires Attunement by a Druid</text>
		<text></text>
		<text>This staff can be wielded as a magic quarterstaff that grants a +2 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with it. While holding it, you have a +2 bonus to spell attack rolls.</text>
