		<text>A bronze horn summons 4d4 + 4 berserkers.  To use the bronze horn, you must be proficient with medium armor.</text>
		<text>If you blow the horn without meeting its requirement, the summoned berserkers attack you. If you meet the requirement, they are friendly to you and your companions and follow your commands.</text>
		<text />
		<text>Source: Dungeon Master's Guide, page 175</text>
