		<text>This tiny object looks like a feather.</text>
		<text></text>
		<text>Fan: If you are on a boat or ship, you can use an action to toss the token up to 10 feet in the air. The token disappears, and a giant flapping fan takes its place. The fan floats and creates a wind strong enough to fill the sails of one ship, increasing its speed by 5 miles per hour for 8 hours. You can dismiss the fan as an action.</text>
		<text />
		<text>Source: Dungeon Master's Guide, page 188</text>
