			<text>You can hold your breath indefinitely while you're not incapacitated.</text>
		</trait>
		<trait>
			<name>Mingle with the Wind</name>
			<text>You can cast the levitate spell once with this trait, requiring no material components, and you regain the ability to cast it this way when you finish a long rest. Constitution is your spellcasting ability for this spell.</text>
		</trait>
		<trait>
			<name>Languages</name>
