			<text>On your turn, you can shift as a bonus action. Shifting lasts for 1 minute or until you end it on your turn as a bonus action.</text>
			<text> </text>
			<text>While shifting, you gain temporary hit points equal to your level + your Constitution bonus (minimum of 1). You also gain a feature that depends on your shifter subrace, described below.</text>
			<text> </text>
			<text>You must finish a short or long rest before you can shift again.</text>
		</trait>
		<trait>
